<p>Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p>
  We are pleased to inform you that your task, "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>", has been marked as completed by <%= @freelancer.name %>.
</p>

<h3>Task Summary:</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %></li>
  <li><strong>Budget:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ") %></li>
  <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @task.status.capitalize %></li>
</ul>

<p>
  You can now review the completed work and provide feedback. Once you're satisfied, feel free to finalize the task to complete the process.
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to 'Review Completed Task', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none;' %>
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for choosing Gighive! If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.
</p>

<p>
  Best Regards,<br>
  <strong>The Gighive Team</strong>
</p>
